avel/travel_notes/detail/luotuo.png \"北京古北水镇小岭四季小家度假别墅沿河景观路分店\")<div class=\"e_hotel_info js_imglist\">\n\n    ## [北京古北水镇小岭四季...](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi18999580-beijinggubeishuizhenxiao)\n<span class=\"price_info\"><span class=\"yuan\"></span>暂无报价</span></div>[](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi18999580-beijinggubeishuizhenxiao)</div><div class=\"b_hot_strategy elselikelook\" id=\"elselikelook\"><div class=\"e_hd\">猜你喜欢</div><div class=\"elselike_more\">共 <span class=\"othernum\">2000</span> 篇，[查看更多](//travel.qunar.com/travelbook/list/北京/hot_heat/1.htm)</div>[前面](#)[后面](#)\n\n*   <div class=\"e_thumb_pic js_download\"><div class=\"pic_info\"><div class=\"pic_info\"><div class=\"day pngfix\">4</div><div class=\"title_wrap\"></div>\n\n    ##### BEIJING￨南方人住进...\n[](/youji/6944927 \"BEIJING￨南方人住进了老胡同，探店一把文艺范儿\")</div>![BEIJING￨南方人住进了老胡同，探店一把文艺范儿](https://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d7/1711/86/5ced3b6a1e66e4b5.jpg_235x187x95_a55f98e1.jpg \"BEIJING￨南方人住进了老胡同，探店一把文艺范儿\")</div><div data-beacon=\"click_strategy_template\" class=\"e_thumb_text js_picLink\"><dl class=\"user_info clrfix\"><dt class=\"avatar\">[![JoyiiF](https://qcommons.qunar.com/headshot/headshotsById/148690688.png?s&amp;ssl=true)](//travel.qunar.com/space/148690688@qunar)</dt><div class=\"text_detail\"><div class=\"name\">[JoyiiF](//travel.qunar.com/space/148690688@qunar \"JoyiiF\")<span> | </span><span class=\"js_time\">2017-10-07</span><span> 出发</span></div><div class=\"list\"><span class=\"list_daynum\">共**4**天</span></div><div class=\"tip_site\">\n\n    途径：北京</div></div></dl></div>\n*   <div class=\"e_thumb_pic js_download\"><div class=\"pic_info\"><div class=\"pic_info\"><div class=\"day pngfix\">6</div><div class=\"title_wrap\"></div>\n\n    ##### 三十年后，意外重温爸...\n[](/youji/7009736 \"三十年后，意外重温爸妈的北京爱情故事「北京5天5夜」\")</div>![三十年后，意外重温爸妈的北京爱情故事「北京5天5夜」](https://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d9/1803/ad/710422fa5e9b87b5.jpg_235x187x95_0a296b9b.jpg \"三十年后，意外重温爸妈的北京爱情故事「北京5天5夜」\")</div><div data-beacon=\"click_strategy_t