tn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![上海城隍庙道观图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"上海城隍庙道观图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263416\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![上海城隍庙道观图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"上海城隍庙道观图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263417\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![上海城隍庙道观图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"上海城隍庙道观图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263420\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n祥云\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![上海城隍庙道观图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"上海城隍庙道观图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263421\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![上海城隍庙道观图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"上海城隍庙道观图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263423\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n富丽堂皇的感觉有木有\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![上海城隍庙道观图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"上海城隍庙道观图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263424\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![上海城隍庙道观图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"上海城隍庙道观图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263425\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![上海城隍庙道观图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"上海城隍庙道观图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263426\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![上海城隍庙道观图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"上海城隍庙道观图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263418\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n逛了一会城隍庙就奔外滩去了，距离不算远，步行十分钟肯定到了\n</div></dd></dl></div></div><div class=\"ops\"><div class=\"inner clrfix\"><div class=\"left\"></div><div class=\"right\">[评论](javascript:;)</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"b_poi_info b_poi_item\" id=\"ele-17145294-4\" data-poitype=\"4\"  poi-id=\"712404\"  data-dist-id=\"299878\" element-type=event><div class=\"top\">\n\n##### <span class=\"iconfont\"></span><div class=\"b_poi_title_box\">[外滩](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi712404-waitan \"外滩\")</div><div class=\"count-bd\"><span class=\"color-red\">5分</span><span class=\"color-gray\">/</span></div>[451篇游记中提到](//travel.qunar.com/travelbook/list/4-waitan-712404.htm)<div data-eleId=\"712404\" class=\"piao_info js_piaoinfo clrfix\"><div class=\"price\">门票<span class=\"pr\">_¥_</span></div>[预订](#)</div>\n<div class=\"info\"><div class=\"main_ct\">\n\n*   <span>门票价格：</span>免费\n*   <span>开放时间：</span>全天\n*   <span>地址：</span>上海市黄浦区中山东一路（临黄浦江）\n*   <span>简介：</span>身倚浦西漫步十里洋场，隔江对望浦东繁华陆家嘴。\n*   [查看详情](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi712404-waitan)<div class=\"triangle\"></div></div></div><div style=\"display:none\" class=\"b_poitext_ad\"></div></div><div class=\"bottom\"><div class=\"e_img_schedule\"><div class=\"imglst\"><div class=\"text js_memo_node\">\n\n全长1.5公里，一路上一幢幢哥特式，罗马式，文艺复兴式，巴洛克式等建筑，中西合璧，风格迥异，把建筑艺术表现得淋漓尽致，所以叫万国建筑博览群\n</div><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263310\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n这是在城隍庙去外滩的路上\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263311\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n转角遇到劳斯莱斯，来一张吧，毕竟贵\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263202\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n走了一会一抬头，诶，这是啥，这么高还有个球，你们当然知道这是啥第一眼看见略兴奋\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263215\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n真是叫人目不暇接\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:453px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263210\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n海关大楼，哥特式大楼，大钟是美国造的，当时花了两千多两白银\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10274139\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n哞这个角度刚刚好\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263218\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263213\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263222\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263207\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n华灯绽放，各式古典建筑就像披上霓裳羽衣，繁华夺目，隔江相望的陆家嘴更是美轮美奂\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263232\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n终于来到这，人不是一般的多，怀着激动的心情，发个微博定个位证明我来过。\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263206\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n江中的游船\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263172\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n经典\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263203\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n外滩走得很快，因为我知道明天我还会再来的，哈哈哈\n</div></dd></dl></div></div><div class=\"ops\"><div class=\"inner clrfix\"><div class=\"left\"></div><div class=\"right\">[评论](javascript:;)</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"b_poi_info b_poi_item\" id=\"ele-17145295-4\" data-poitype=\"4\"  poi-id=\"5740177\"  data-dist-id=\"299878\" element-type=event><div class=\"top\">\n\n##### <span class=\"iconfont\"></span><div class=\"b_poi_title_box\">[外白渡桥](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi5740177-waibaiduqiao \"外白渡桥\")</div><div class=\"count-bd\"><span class=\"color-red\">5分</span><span class=\"color-gray\">/</span></div>[67篇游记中提到](//travel.qunar.com/travelbook/list/4-waibaiduqiao-5740177.htm)<div data-eleId=\"5740177\" class=\"piao_info js_piaoinfo clrfix\"><div class=\"price\">门票<span class=\"pr\">_¥_</span></div>[预订](#)</div>\n<div class=\"info\"><div class=\"main_ct\">\n\n*   <span>门票价格：</span>免费\n*   <span>开放时间：</span>全天\n*   <span>地址：</span>上海市黄浦区北苏州路111\n*   <span>简介：</span>上海标志性建筑之一，老上海题材影视剧取景地。\n*   [查看详情](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi5740177-waibaiduqiao)<div class=\"triangle\"></div></div></div><div style=\"display:none\" class=\"b_poitext_ad\"></div></div><div class=\"bottom\"><div class=\"e_img_schedule\"><div class=\"imglst\"><div class=\"text js_memo_node\">\n\n中国第一座全钢结构铆接桥梁，连接苏州河两岸。\n</div><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:453px\">![外白渡桥图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外白渡桥图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263227\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n终于走到了，脚已经酸得不行了\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外白渡桥图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外白渡桥图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263223\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n怎么样，怎么样，个人觉得还可以\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外白渡桥图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外白渡桥图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263230\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n到了当年依萍跳桥的地方\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外白渡桥图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外白渡桥图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263555\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n为了拍这个带了两个相机，有点感觉吧\n</div></dd></dl></div></div><div class=\"ops\"><div class=\"inner clrfix\"><div class=\"left\"></div><div class=\"right\">[评论](javascript:;)</div></div></div></div></div></div><!-- /period_ct end --></div><!-- /e_day end --><!-- e_day start --><div id=\"day-17353335\" data-dayidx=\"day-17353335\" class=\"e_day day_style0 day-17353335\">\n\n#### <dl class=\"day_title\"><dt class=\"clrfix\"><div class=\"style\"></div><div class=\"text\">第2天</div></dt></dl>\n<!-- period_ct start --><div class=\"period_ct\"><div class=\"b_poi_info b_poi_item\" id=\"ele-17145296-4\" data-poitype=\"4\"  poi-id=\"5475557\"  data-dist-id=\"299878\" element-type=event><div class=\"top\">\n\n##### <span class=\"iconfont\"></span><div class=\"b_poi_title_box\">[甜爱路](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi5475557-tianailu \"甜爱路\")</div><div class=\"count-bd\"><span class=\"color-red\">4分</span><span class=\"color-gray\">/</span></div>[39篇游记中提到](//travel.qunar.com/travelbook/list/4-tianailu-5475557.htm)<div data-eleId=\"5475557\" class=\"piao_info js_piaoinfo clrfix\"><div class=\"price\">门票<span class=\"pr\">_¥_</span></div>[预订](#)</div>\n<div class=\"info\"><div class=\"main_ct\">\n\n*   <span>门票价格：</span>免费\n*   <span>开放时间：</span>全天\n*   <span>电话：</span>021-62189993\n*   <span>地址：</span>上海市虹口区甜爱路\n*   <span>简介：</span>上海最浪漫的马路，在爱心邮筒给你的TA寄出盖有爱心邮戳的信函。\n*   [查看详情](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi5475557-tianailu)<div class=\"triangle\"></div></div></div><div style=\"display:none\" class=\"b_poitext_ad\"></div></div><div class=\"bottom\"><div class=\"e_img_schedule\"><div class=\"imglst\"><div class=\"text js_memo_node\">\n\n第一天起的最早，8点就出发了，按计划前往甜爱路，距离旅店不远，走了大约15分钟就到了，甜爱路是情侣必来的地方，在这里见证了太多的爱情故事，单身狗就不要来了，这个时候是我最希望有个旅伴的时候，来个妹子来拍人像，简直完美，恰到好处。So&nbsp;Sad\n</div><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![甜爱路图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"甜爱路图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263463\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n听见这个名字就甜蜜，可惜。。。\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![甜爱路图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"甜爱路图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263451\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n甜爱路上少有的咖啡馆，来的太早还没开门\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![甜爱路图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"甜爱路图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263567\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![甜爱路图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"甜爱路图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263568\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n路上一对情侣都没有。。。什么情况，是因为我来的太早吗？\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![甜爱路图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"甜爱路图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263454\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![甜爱路图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"甜爱路图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263455\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n清晨的甜爱路静谧得很，只有少数的车辆和行人\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![甜爱路图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"甜爱路图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263458\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![甜爱路图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"甜爱路图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263459\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n大清早的也出来散步了，早起的猫儿有鱼吃\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![甜爱路图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"甜爱路图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263460\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![甜爱路图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"甜爱路图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263461\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n爱心邮箱，投在这里的信都会盖上一枚特有的爱心邮戳，但是只在下午开箱，想投的朋友注意开箱时间。\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![甜爱路图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"甜爱路图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263462\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n最后看见这幅画，很漂亮\n</div></dd></dl></div></div><div class=\"ops\"><div class=\"inner clrfix\"><div class=\"left\"></div><div class=\"right\">[评论](javascript:;)</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"b_poi_info b_poi_item\" id=\"ele-17145297-4\" data-poitype=\"4\"  poi-id=\"710405\"  data-dist-id=\"299878\" element-type=event><div class=\"top\">\n\n##### <span class=\"iconfont\"></span><div class=\"b_poi_title_box\">[多伦路文化名人街](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi710405-duolunluwenhuamingren \"多伦路文化名人街\")</div><div class=\"count-bd\"><span class=\"color-red\">4分</span><span class=\"color-gray\">/</span></div>[23篇游记中提到](//travel.qunar.com/travelbook/list/4-duolunluwenhuamingren-710405.htm)<div data-eleId=\"710405\" class=\"piao_info js_piaoinfo clrfix\"><div class=\"price\">门票<span class=\"pr\">_¥_</span></div>[预订](#)</div>\n<div class=\"info\"><div class=\"main_ct\">\n\n*   <span>门票价格：</span>免费\n*   <span>开放时间：</span>全天\n*   <span>电话：</span>021-56668801\n*   <span>地址：</span>上海市虹口区多伦路（东江湾路至四川北路）\n*   <span>简介：</span>参观鲁迅、茅盾、郭沫若等名人故居，在复古的洋楼老街散步拍照。\n*   [查看详情](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi710405-duolunluwenhuamingren)<div class=\"triangle\"></div></div></div><div style=\"display:none\" class=\"b_poitext_ad\"></div></div><div class=\"bottom\"><div class=\"e_img_schedule\"><div class=\"imglst\"><div class=\"text js_memo_node\">\n\n距离甜爱路很近，走一会就到了，这是一条500多米的小街，鲁迅，矛盾，郭沫若，叶圣陶都在这活动过。。。有着浓厚的文化气息。\n</div><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![多伦路文化名人街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"多伦路文化名人街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263465\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n大门，来的时候经过这里，竟然没发现它\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![多伦路文化名人街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"多伦路文化名人街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263466\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n刚进去，各种古玩店，也是因为来的太早，大多数店还没开门，游客也很少\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![多伦路文化名人街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"多伦路文化名人街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263467\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n特点就是每户人家都会支出来架子晾衣服\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![多伦路文化名人街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"多伦路文化名人街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263468\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![多伦路文化名人街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"多伦路文化名人街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263469\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![多伦路文化名人街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"多伦路文化名人街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263471\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n一座教堂，门口写着上帝爱世人\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![多伦路文化名人街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"多伦路文化名人街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263472\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n来旅游的老两口，互相给对方拍照，老伴老伴，老来的伴\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![多伦路文化名人街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"多伦路文化名人街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263473\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![多伦路文化名人街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"多伦路文化名人街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263474\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n鲁迅故里，门口的雕像，游客都会坐上去合照，可惜我是一个人，没人给我拍。。。\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![多伦路文化名人街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"多伦路文化名人街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263475\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![多伦路文化名人街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"多伦路文化名人街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263476\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n门口的花~\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![多伦路文化名人街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"多伦路文化名人街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263477\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n在这碰个老大爷，也是一口地道的上海话，看我在这拍照，就告诉我拍这种文化气息，就要到思南路和武康路去\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![多伦路文化名人街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"多伦路文化名人街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263478\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n天气越来越好\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![多伦路文化名人街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"多伦路文化名人街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263479\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![多伦路文化名人街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"多伦路文化名人街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263481\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n转了一圈，又回到这里\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![多伦路文化名人街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"多伦路文化名人街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263482\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n由于天气不错，临时改了计划，决定浦东走起\n</div></dd></dl></div></div><div class=\"ops\"><div class=\"inner clrfix\"><div class=\"left\"></div><div class=\"right\">[评论](javascript:;)</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"b_poi_info b_poi_item\" id=\"ele-17145298-4\" data-poitype=\"4\"  poi-id=\"707203\"  data-dist-id=\"299878\" element-type=event><div class=\"top\">\n\n##### <span class=\"iconfont\"></span><div class=\"b_poi_title_box\">[鲁迅公园](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi707203-luxungongyuan \"鲁迅公园\")</div><div class=\"count-bd\"><span class=\"color-red\">5分</span><span class=\"color-gray\">/</span></div>[17篇游记中提到](//travel.qunar.com/travelbook/list/4-luxungongyuan-707203.htm)<div data-eleId=\"707203\" class=\"piao_info js_piaoinfo clrfix\"><div class=\"price\">门票<span class=\"pr\">_¥_</span></div>[预订](#)</div>\n<div class=\"info\"><div class=\"main_ct\">\n\n*   <span>门票价格：</span>免费\n*   <span>开放时间：</span>9:00-16:00\n*   <span>电话：</span>021-65401561\n*   <span>地址：</span>上海市虹口区四川北路2288号\n*   <span>简介：</span>鲁迅先生曾经常来此散步，瞻仰鲁迅先生之墓，了解他的生平。\n*   [查看详情](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi707203-luxungongyuan)<div class=\"triangle\"></div></div></div><div style=\"display:none\" class=\"b_poitext_ad\"></div></div><div class=\"bottom\"><div class=\"e_img_schedule\"><div class=\"imglst\"><div class=\"text js_memo_node\">\n\n只是路过。。。当时内急，来这公共厕所方便一下，走到虹口足球场坐的地铁\n</div></div></div><div class=\"ops\"><div class=\"inner clrfix\"><div class=\"left\"></div><div class=\"right\">[评论](javascript:;)</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"b_poi_info b_poi_item\" id=\"ele-17145299-8\" data-poitype=\"8\"  poi-id=\"0\"  data-dist-id=\"299878\" element-type=event><div class=\"top\">\n\n##### <span class=\"iconfont\"></span><div class=\"b_poi_title_box\">南京路步行街</div><div class=\"count-bd\"><span class=\"color-red\">5分</span></div>\n<div class=\"info\"><div class=\"main_ct\">\n\n*   <span>开放时间：</span>全天\n*   <span>电话：</span>021-51099782\n*   <span>地址：</span>上海市黄浦区（西起西藏中路,东至河南中路）\n*   <span>简介：</span>南京路步行街是上海著名的购物场所，来这里你既能感受到旧时代的烙印，又能感受到新时代的发展。<div class=\"triangle\"></div></div></div><div style=\"display:none\" class=\"b_poitext_ad\"></div></div><div class=\"bottom\"><div class=\"e_img_schedule\"><div class=\"imglst\"><div class=\"text js_memo_node\">\n\n又来到这。。。也只是路过\n</div><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![南京路步行街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"南京路步行街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263483\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n每一代，都是一个时代&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;听着这么耳熟，像是小时代里的台词，在这小小的时代里。。。巴拉巴拉什么的记不得了\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![南京路步行街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"南京路步行街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263484\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n其实这都是给我一个爱外国帅哥的女（bai）同（qian）学（wen）照的\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![南京路步行街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"南京路步行街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263485\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![南京路步行街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"南京路步行街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263486\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl></div></div><div class=\"ops\"><div class=\"inner clrfix\"><div class=\"left\"></div><div class=\"right\">[评论_(1)_](javascript:;)</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"b_poi_info b_poi_item\" id=\"ele-17145300-4\" data-poitype=\"4\"  poi-id=\"712404\"  data-dist-id=\"299878\" element-type=event><div class=\"top\">\n\n##### <span class=\"iconfont\"></span><div class=\"b_poi_title_box\">[外滩](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi712404-waitan \"外滩\")</div><div class=\"count-bd\"><span class=\"color-red\">5分</span><span class=\"color-gray\">/</span></div>[451篇游记中提到](//travel.qunar.com/travelbook/list/4-waitan-712404.htm)<div data-eleId=\"712404\" class=\"piao_info js_piaoinfo clrfix\"><div class=\"price\">门票<span class=\"pr\">_¥_</span></div>[预订](#)</div>\n<div class=\"info\"><div class=\"main_ct\">\n\n*   <span>门票价格：</span>免费\n*   <span>开放时间：</span>全天\n*   <span>地址：</span>上海市黄浦区中山东一路（临黄浦江）\n*   <span>简介：</span>身倚浦西漫步十里洋场，隔江对望浦东繁华陆家嘴。\n*   [查看详情](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi712404-waitan)<div class=\"triangle\"></div></div></div><div style=\"display:none\" class=\"b_poitext_ad\"></div></div><div class=\"bottom\"><div class=\"e_img_schedule\"><div class=\"imglst\"><div class=\"text js_memo_node\">\n\n再一次来是为了看看她白天时的样子\n</div><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263560\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n浦发银行，只能说壮观\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263571\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10287738\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n这个用手机照的\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263573\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263572\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n外滩拍婚纱照的真是多，几乎走几步就会看到一对，都是辣么美，真是苦了摄影师，更苦了摄影助理，各种摆造型，各种抬裙子。。。\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263574\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:453px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263578\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n瞧瞧这肌肉\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263575\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263579\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n2块过江，蛮划算的\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![外滩图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"外滩图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263580\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n环球金融中心刚刚露出一角\n</div></dd></dl></div></div><div class=\"ops\"><div class=\"inner clrfix\"><div class=\"left\"></div><div class=\"right\">[评论](javascript:;)</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"b_poi_info b_poi_item\" id=\"ele-17155489-4\" data-poitype=\"4\"  poi-id=\"714169\"  data-dist-id=\"299878\" element-type=event><div class=\"top\">\n\n##### <span class=\"iconfont\"></span><div class=\"b_poi_title_box\">[滨江大道](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi714169-binjiangdadao \"滨江大道\")</div><div class=\"count-bd\"><span class=\"color-red\">5分</span><span class=\"color-gray\">/</span></div>[23篇游记中提到](//travel.qunar.com/travelbook/list/4-binjiangdadao-714169.htm)<div data-eleId=\"714169\" class=\"piao_info js_piaoinfo clrfix\"><div class=\"price\">门票<span class=\"pr\">_¥_</span></div>[预订](#)</div>\n<div class=\"info\"><div class=\"main_ct\">\n\n*   <span>门票价格：</span>免费\n*   <span>开放时间：</span>全天\n*   <span>电话：</span>021-58871096,021-58875487\n*   <span>地址：</span>上海市浦东新区滨江大道\n*   <span>简介：</span>与外滩隔江相望的人行步道，白天漫步江边，夜晚欣赏两岸夜景。\n*   [查看详情](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi714169-binjiangdadao)<div class=\"triangle\"></div></div></div><div style=\"display:none\" class=\"b_poitext_ad\"></div></div><div class=\"bottom\"><div class=\"e_img_schedule\"><div class=\"imglst\"><div class=\"text js_memo_node\">\n\n上了岸，沿着路，抬头看见东方明珠就有了方向，嗯，走。可能这个定位有点问题，总之就是刚上岸以后得那条道\n</div><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:453px\">![滨江大道图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"滨江大道图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263505\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n真是高耸入云，在建的上海中心，高度超过了环球金融中心\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![滨江大道图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"滨江大道图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263506\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n外国的一家四口来旅游，不得不说，基因真是好，姐姐和弟弟美得不要不要的\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![滨江大道图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"滨江大道图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263508\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n上海的香格里拉，怎么感觉和我家的长得一样\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![滨江大道图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"滨江大道图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263509\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n震旦，金灿灿一片\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![滨江大道图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"滨江大道图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263510\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl></div></div><div class=\"ops\"><div class=\"inner clrfix\"><div class=\"left\"></div><div class=\"right\">[评论](javascript:;)</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"b_poi_info b_poi_item\" id=\"ele-17145302-4\" data-poitype=\"4\"  poi-id=\"709275\"  data-dist-id=\"299878\" element-type=event><div class=\"top\">\n\n##### <span class=\"iconfont\"></span><div class=\"b_poi_title_box\">[东方明珠](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi709275-dongfangmingzhu \"东方明珠\")</div><div class=\"count-bd\"><span class=\"color-red\">5分</span><span class=\"color-gray\">/</span></div>[215篇游记中提到](//travel.qunar.com/travelbook/list/4-dongfangmingzhu-709275.htm)<div data-eleId=\"709275\" class=\"piao_info js_piaoinfo clrfix\"><div class=\"price\">门票<span class=\"pr\">_¥_</span></div>[预订](#)</div>\n<div class=\"info\"><div class=\"main_ct\">\n\n*   <span>门票价格：</span>160元\n*   <span>开放时间：</span>8:00-22:00\n*   <span>电话：</span>021-58792888\n*   <span>地址：</span>上海市浦东新区陆家嘴世纪大道1号\n*   <span>简介：</span>在259米高的全透明观光廊上，360度欣赏申城夜景。\n*   [查看详情](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi709275-dongfangmingzhu)<div class=\"triangle\"></div></div></div><div style=\"display:none\" class=\"b_poitext_ad\"></div></div><div class=\"bottom\"><div class=\"e_img_schedule\"><div class=\"imglst\"><div class=\"text js_memo_node\">\n\n学生票不打折学生票不打折学生票不打折！！！重要的事说三遍，本来都想不上去了，结果想来都来了，不差这点了，硬着头皮买了票\n</div><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272557\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n220~到顶，其实说实话不建议走到顶，前提是你有去环球金融中心的计划\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:453px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272551\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n江泽民题的字\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10268578\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n在它脚下仰望\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272546\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n进门排队\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10273174\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n刚刚不是排队，这才是排队，电梯每次上十个人左右\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:453px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10269616\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n细看真是巧夺天工，不禁赞叹先人的手艺，赞\n\n这都是在历史陈列馆里的，照片顺序有些问题\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10273150\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272450\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n走到这的时候旁边那哥们说这不是我练车时候用的桑塔纳吗，怎么摆这了？哈哈哈有木有觉得很好笑，好吧文字不能重现他当时的语气\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272454\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10269718\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272456\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n这些讲的都是上海汽车的发展\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10269810\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n这是电梯井，本来想修的梦幻点\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10269925\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n小女孩她爸爸在给她拍照，我也抓拍了一张\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272457\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n这不是我\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272459\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n并没有觉得很恐怖\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272458\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n原来我不恐高\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272462\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n同样的爱好\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272464\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272472\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n俯瞰外白渡桥\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272511\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n汽车像玩具，行人像蚂蚁\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10273161\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n像不像爸爸和儿子\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272515\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n绕了一圈才找到，瞬间浓浓的思乡之情\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10273173\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272489\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n远方的游客，带着父母一家来魔都，这里的魅力可见一斑\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272497\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272527\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n竟然高出这么多\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272524\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n调皮的老外\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272526\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n照不到风景，只能拍拍人了\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272519\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n太空舱，照相是不行，只能来感受感受\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![东方明珠图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"东方明珠图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10269566\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n全球仅此一家，可口可乐餐厅\n</div></dd></dl></div>\n\n[查看全部](#)\n</div><div class=\"ops\"><div class=\"inner clrfix\"><div class=\"left\"></div><div class=\"right\">[评论_(1)_](javascript:;)</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"b_poi_info b_poi_item\" id=\"ele-17145303-8\" data-poitype=\"8\"  poi-id=\"0\"  data-dist-id=\"299878\" element-type=event><div class=\"top\">\n\n##### <span class=\"iconfont\"></span><div class=\"b_poi_title_box\">南京路步行街</div><div class=\"count-bd\"><span class=\"color-red\">5分</span></div>\n<div class=\"info\"><div class=\"main_ct\">\n\n*   <span>开放时间：</span>全天\n*   <span>电话：</span>021-51099782\n*   <span>地址：</span>上海市黄浦区（西起西藏中路,东至河南中路）\n*   <span>简介：</span>南京路步行街是上海著名的购物场所，来这里你既能感受到旧时代的烙印，又能感受到新时代的发展。<div class=\"triangle\"></div></div></div><div style=\"display:none\" class=\"b_poitext_ad\"></div></div><div class=\"bottom\"><div class=\"e_img_schedule\"><div class=\"imglst\"><div class=\"text js_memo_node\">\n\n来这又是为了坐地铁\n</div><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![南京路步行街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"南京路步行街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263556\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![南京路步行街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"南京路步行街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263557\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![南京路步行街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"南京路步行街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10263558\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n都这个点了，依旧全！是！人！！！\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![南京路步行街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"南京路步行街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272769\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![南京路步行街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"南京路步行街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272764\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\nFOREVER&nbsp;21，对这个感情颇深\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![南京路步行街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"南京路步行街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272758\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n上海快节奏的生活，会压得人喘不过气来\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![南京路步行街图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"南京路步行街图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272750\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n匆忙的行人，疲惫的眼神，心中的一份信念，文不对图\n</div></dd></dl></div></div><div class=\"ops\"><div class=\"inner clrfix\"><div class=\"left\"></div><div class=\"right\">[评论](javascript:;)</div></div></div></div></div></div><!-- /period_ct end --></div><!-- /e_day end --><!-- e_day start --><div id=\"day-17353336\" data-dayidx=\"day-17353336\" class=\"e_day day_style0 day-17353336\">\n\n#### <dl class=\"day_title\"><dt class=\"clrfix\"><div class=\"style\"></div><div class=\"text\">第3天</div></dt></dl>\n<!-- period_ct start --><div class=\"period_ct\"><div class=\"b_poi_info b_poi_item\" id=\"ele-17145304-4\" data-poitype=\"4\"  poi-id=\"3710932\"  data-dist-id=\"299878\" element-type=event><div class=\"top\">\n\n##### <span class=\"iconfont\"></span><div class=\"b_poi_title_box\">[1933老场坊](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi3710932-1933laochangfang \"1933老场坊\")</div><div class=\"count-bd\"><span class=\"color-red\">5分</span><span class=\"color-gray\">/</span></div>[47篇游记中提到](//travel.qunar.com/travelbook/list/4-1933laochangfang-3710932.htm)<div data-eleId=\"3710932\" class=\"piao_info js_piaoinfo clrfix\"><div class=\"price\">门票<span class=\"pr\">_¥_</span></div>[预订](#)</div>\n<div class=\"info\"><div class=\"main_ct\">\n\n*   <span>门票价格：</span>免费\n*   <span>开放时间：</span>9:00-22:00\n*   <span>电话：</span>021-68881933,4008881933\n*   <span>地址：</span>虹口区溧阳路611号\n*   <span>简介：</span>由宰牲场改造的创意园区，时尚餐厅、奢牌秀场汇聚于此。\n*   [查看详情](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi3710932-1933laochangfang)<div class=\"triangle\"></div></div></div><div style=\"display:none\" class=\"b_poitext_ad\"></div></div><div class=\"bottom\"><div class=\"e_img_schedule\"><div class=\"imglst\"><div class=\"text js_memo_node\">\n\n九点出门。。。（前一天太累）出门就发现天气不好，虽然早有心理准备，但还是感觉去球。但是影响并不大，而且我还比较希望今天下雨，后面就知道原因了。\n\n1933真的不太好找，距离地铁站挺远\n\n看了好多在这拍的时尚大片，为了找找小时代里的感觉，自己也想文艺一把，所以来了，并没叫我失望\n\n这里曾是远东最大的屠宰场，造型特殊，外方内方。伞形柱、廊桥、旋梯、牛道相互交错，但又井井有条，着实有着非常独特的味道。\n</div><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272606\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n刚到门口天气就阴得不行，心想快拍一下门面，一会下了雨就不好拍了，结果我想的完全正确\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272620\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n貌似一个公司员工来这玩撕名牌加寻宝\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272717\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n刚进来外面就下大了\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272640\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n牛道\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:453px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272644\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n很多创意文化公司都入驻在这里，也许这样的环境能激发更多的灵感吧\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272645\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272646\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272650\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n客官进来坐啊。。。可惜并没有小二\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272651\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272665\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272678\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272688\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n这种建筑风格真是让人耳目一新\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272695\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272706\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n牛道。。。之前走牛的地方？\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272710\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n雨水会流进来，但是过了这么多年并没有看见雨水侵蚀的痕迹，建筑质量绝对杠杠滴\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272721\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272723\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272731\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n一楼的餐厅\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![1933老场坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"1933老场坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10272738\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n上海处处都有的星巴克在这有了些不一样的感觉\n</div></dd></dl></div></div><div class=\"ops\"><div class=\"inner clrfix\"><div class=\"left\"></div><div class=\"right\">[评论](javascript:;)</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"b_poi_info b_poi_item\" id=\"ele-17145305-4\" data-poitype=\"4\"  poi-id=\"716890\"  data-dist-id=\"299878\" element-type=event><div class=\"top\">\n\n##### <span class=\"iconfont\"></span><div class=\"b_poi_title_box\">[田子坊石库门](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi716890-tianzifangshikumen \"田子坊石库门\")</div>[23篇游记中提到](//travel.qunar.com/travelbook/list/4-tianzifangshikumen-716890.htm)<div data-eleId=\"716890\" class=\"piao_info js_piaoinfo clrfix\"><div class=\"price\">门票<span class=\"pr\">_¥_</span></div>[预订](#)</div>\n<div class=\"info\"><div class=\"main_ct\">\n\n*   <span>门票价格：</span>免费\n*   <span>开放时间：</span>全天\n*   <span>地址：</span>上海市黄浦区绍兴路96弄\n*   [查看详情](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi716890-tianzifangshikumen)<div class=\"triangle\"></div></div></div><div style=\"display:none\" class=\"b_poitext_ad\"></div></div><div class=\"bottom\"><div class=\"e_img_schedule\"><div class=\"imglst\"><div class=\"text js_memo_node\">\n\n打算去石库门逛一逛的，结果刚到了这老乡妹子就打电话说约田子坊，没办法，只能去了，谁叫我之前答应她一起玩的呢正好肚子饿了，找家快餐店一边吃一边等她一会。\n</div><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:510px\">![田子坊石库门图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"田子坊石库门图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10273839\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n里面是自选餐厅那种，看见这块肉我就迈不动脚了，累了两天快快补偿一下\n\n不得不说，真是挺香，满足\n</div></dd></dl></div></div><div class=\"ops\"><div class=\"inner clrfix\"><div class=\"left\"></div><div class=\"right\">[评论](javascript:;)</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"b_poi_info b_poi_item\" id=\"ele-17145306-4\" data-poitype=\"4\"  poi-id=\"722972\"  data-dist-id=\"299878\" element-type=event><div class=\"top\">\n\n##### <span class=\"iconfont\"></span><div class=\"b_poi_title_box\">[田子坊](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi722972-tianzifang \"田子坊\")</div><div class=\"count-bd\"><span class=\"color-red\">5分</span><span class=\"color-gray\">/</span></div>[215篇游记中提到](//travel.qunar.com/travelbook/list/4-tianzifang-722972.htm)<div data-eleId=\"722972\" class=\"piao_info js_piaoinfo clrfix\"><div class=\"price\">门票<span class=\"pr\">_¥_</span></div>[预订](#)</div>\n<div class=\"info\"><div class=\"main_ct\">\n\n*   <span>门票价格：</span>免费\n*   <span>开放时间：</span>全天\n*   <span>电话：</span>021-54657531\n*   <span>地址：</span>上海市黄浦区泰康路210弄\n*   <span>简介：</span>穿梭在上海小弄堂里，逛逛复古小店和文人工作室。\n*   [查看详情](https://travel.qunar.com/p-oi722972-tianzifang)<div class=\"triangle\"></div></div></div><div style=\"display:none\" class=\"b_poitext_ad\"></div></div><div class=\"bottom\"><div class=\"e_img_schedule\"><div class=\"imglst\"><div class=\"text js_memo_node\">\n\n这里果然是文艺气息的发源地，里面典型的上海弄堂，道路两边的小店各具特色，照了很多照片，每一张都不舍得扔啊\n</div><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![田子坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"田子坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10276268\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n田子坊对面是日月光中心，估计是为了沾沾田子坊的人气\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![田子坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"田子坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10276301\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n琉璃博物馆，琉璃的宫殿，晚上开灯之后美炸\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![田子坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"田子坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10276310\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n尝尝鲜\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![田子坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"田子坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10276278\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n\n田子坊地图。。。看懂了，但还是迷路\n</div></dd></dl><dl class=\"js_memo_node\"><dt style=\"width:680px\">![田子坊图片](https://source.qunarzz.com/site/images/travel/finish/space_3nd.png \"田子坊图片\")<div class=\"img_btn_wrap\"><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_digg iconfont\" data-id=\"10276335\"><span class=\"num\"></span></span><span class=\"img_btn img_btn_comment iconfont\"></span></div></dt><dd class=\"img_txt_wrap\"><span class=\"tri\"></span><div class=\"img_txt\">\n